OL,6,FA man who stole #55,000 worth of goods
OL,7,Ffrom Boots stores in Wales and England
OL,8,Fin a "staggering" six-month crime
OL,9,Fspree was caught following a UK-wide
OL,10,Fpolice initiative.
OL,12,FOpal, a central policing intelligence
OL,13,Fservice, launched a new specific team
OL,14,Fto target organised retail crime in
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FTheir work led to the arrest of
OL,18,FAlexandru-Iulian Dima.
