OL,3,CMan stole #55,000 worth of goods from
OL,4,CBoots in 'staggering' crime spree
OL,6,FDima, 25, stole from Boots branches in
OL,7,FPontypridd, Haverfordwest and Cardiff
OL,8,FBay - with the value of the thefts
OL,9,Ftotalling several thousand pounds on
OL,10,Feach occasion.
OL,12,FOpal identified his pattern of
OL,13,Foffending, which took place in areas
OL,14,Fcovered by different police forces.
OL,16,FSouth Wales Police then took on the
OL,17,Finvestigation and Dima pleaded guilty
OL,18,Fto six counts of theft and was
OL,19,Fsentenced to four years in prison.
