OL,6,FAnother offender, Brendon Brain, stole
OL,7,Fmore than #33,000 worth of goods
OL,8,Fincluding electricals, sunglasses,
OL,9,Ffragrances and baby products in areas
OL,10,Fincluding south Wales.
