OL,4,CBoots in 'staggering' crime spree
OL,6,FBetween May and August 2024, Opal's
OL,7,Fserious organised retail crime group
OL,8,Fidentified 152 "high harm individuals"
OL,9,Finvolved in organised retail crime and
OL,10,Faffected 23 arrests impacting at least
OL,11,F16 businesses.
OL,13,FStephanie Coombes, head of
OL,14,Fintelligence at Opal, said: "Opal has
OL,15,Fbeen carrying out this role for other
OL,16,Fcrime types for a number of years and
OL,17,Fwe have seen significant successes
OL,18,Ffrom having a national overview of
OL,19,Fwhat's happening in the organised
OL,20,Fcrime world.
