OL,3,CMan stole #55,000 worth of goods from
OL,4,CBoots in 'staggering' crime spree
OL,6,F"As we've seen, organised crime groups
OL,7,Fmay be targeting one retailer using
OL,8,Fthe same tactics across multiple
OL,9,Fregions and without a national team to
OL,10,Fbring together that information, we
OL,11,Fcould have several police forces each
OL,12,Flooking into the same group.
OL,14,F"Our role is vital in centralising
OL,15,Fintelligence, building strong evidence
OL,16,Fpackages and then working with the
OL,17,Frelevant force/s to deal with these
OL,18,Fhigh harm offenders.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
