OL,3,CMan stole #55,000 worth of goods from
OL,4,CBoots in 'staggering' crime spree
OL,6,F"Our work can be as light touch as
OL,7,Fputting CCTV images through the Police
OL,8,FNational Database to identify an
OL,9,Findividual or as extensive as building
OL,10,Fa detailed intelligence package of
OL,11,Foffending across multiple areas and
OL,12,Fretailers but either way it's proving
OL,13,Fextremely effective.
OL,15,F"For far too long these groups have
OL,16,Fbeen damaging retailers and
OL,17,Fcommunities with thefts reaching
OL,18,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds and we
OL,19,Fare now quite literally ensuring they
OL,20,Fhave nowhere to hide."
